OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy across the north tonight with
OL,7,Ffurther outbreaks of light rain
OL,8,Ffeeding onto windward coasts, and
OL,9,Fperhaps the odd shower clipping East
OL,10,FAnglia too. Otherwise, long clear
OL,11,Fspells with the odd fog patch possible
OL,12,Fin prone spots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FStaying cloudy and cool in
OL,15,Fthe far north on Wednesday with light
OL,16,Fshowers possible. Dry and sunny
OL,17,Felsewhere with some very warm sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
